<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What is the AI Content Generator?</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The Generate Content feature uses <strong><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/ai/generative-ai/nova/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Amazon Nova Pro<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a></strong> to create draft content based on your prompts. It helps content editors:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>Draft service pages</strong> quickly from a brief description</li>
  <li><strong>Generate news articles</strong> and announcements</li>
  <li><strong>Create how-to guides</strong> for residents</li>
  <li><strong>Save time</strong> on routine content tasks</li>
</ul>

<div class="govuk-warning-text">
  <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
  <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
    AI-generated content should always be reviewed and edited before publishing.
    The AI is a writing assistant, not a replacement for human judgement.
  </strong>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How to generate content</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Open any content page for editing</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Navigate to Content &gt; find a page &gt; click Edit
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Look for the AI Assistant bar</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Above the content editor, you'll see buttons for "Generate Content" and "Simplify"
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Click "Generate Content"</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      This opens the AI Writing Assistant dialog
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Enter your prompt</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Describe what content you want. Be specific about topic, audience, and key points.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Click Generate</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Wait a few seconds while <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/ai/generative-ai/nova/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Amazon Nova Pro<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> generates your content
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Review and insert</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Read through the result, then click "Insert" to add it to your page, or "Regenerate" to try again
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

